<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('./partials/css/bootstrap.ejs') %>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ionn.</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="https://i.ibb.co/Tx2ScBj6/favicon.jpg">
    <style>
        nav:empty, .navbar:empty {
            display: none;
        }
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            color: #23272b;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 40px 32px;
            margin-top: 48px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(60,72,88,0.12), 0 1.5px 4px rgba(60,72,88,0.08);
        }
        h2, h3 {
            color: #2d3a4a;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        p {
            color: #4a5568;
            font-size: 1.08em;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }
        .card {
            background: #f5f7fa;
            color: #23272b;
            border: 1.5px solid #e0e4ea;
            border-radius: 14px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(60,72,88,0.08);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            min-height: 420px;
        }
        .card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(79,140,255,0.13);
            transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.02);
        }
        .card-title {
            color: #2d3a4a;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4f8cff 60%, #3762c2 100%);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            padding: 10px 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(79,140,255,0.08);
            transition: background 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            color: #fff !important;
            opacity: 1 !important;
            visibility: visible !important;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3762c2 60%, #4f8cff 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(79,140,255,0.15);
        }
        .card-img-top {
            background: #e9ecef;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-top-left-radius: 14px;
            border-top-right-radius: 14px;
            height: 240px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        a, a:visited {
            color: #4f8cff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .row.mt-3 {
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .card-body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            flex: 1 1 auto;
        }
        .mt-auto {
            margin-top: auto !important;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 18px 6px;
                margin-top: 18px;
            }
            .card {
                width: 100% !important;
                margin: 0 0 18px 0 !important;
            }
            .card-img-top {
                height: 180px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('./partials/components/nav.ejs') %>
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h2 class="mt-2">Welcome to Ionn.</h2>
        <br>
        <p>
            Igniting Innovation, Crafted by Students<br>
            We're a passionate and driven company, entirely owned and operated by a dedicated team of students. Our story began with a simple, yet powerful belief: that innovative ideas, no matter how ambitious, deserve to see the light of day. We pour our hearts and countless hours into transforming imaginative concepts into tangible, impactful solutions.
            <br><br>
            Every project we embrace is a testament to our commitment to hard work, meticulous attention to detail, and a relentless pursuit of excellence. We thrive on challenges, constantly pushing the boundaries of what's possible to create unique and effective experiences. We're not just developing products; we're building a foundation for the future, one inspired creation at a time.
        </p>
        <h3 style="margin-top: 20px;">Latest Blogs</h3>
        <br>
        <div class="row mt-3">
            <% blogs.forEach(blog => { %>
                <div class="card mx-2" style="width: 18rem;">
                    <img src="<%=blog.coverImage%>" class="card-img-top" alt="anime image">
                    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                        <h5 class="card-title"><%=blog.title.slice(0,20)%></h5>
                        <p class="card-text"><%=blog.content.slice(0,100)%>...</p>
                        <div class="mt-auto">
                            <a href="/blog/view/<%=blog._id%>" class="btn btn-primary w-100">Read More</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <% }) %>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%- include('./partials/js/bootstrap.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>